            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The ground states of nuclides are stable, so the",
                "statistical method was used to determine their cross",
                "sections of formation. The consequence of this is the",
                "low accuracy (~30%) of the obtained value of the",
                "isomeric ratio, since it is determined by the errors",
                "of absolutization of both the measured and calculated",
                "cross sections."
